! 点积

$$
\bm{A}\cdot\bm{B}=\sum_{i}A_{\cdots,i}B_{i,\cdots}
$$

!! 双点积

$$
\bm{A}:\bm{B}=\sum_{i,j}A_{\cdots,i,j}B_{j,i,\cdots}
$$

!! 三点积

$$
\bm{A}\vdots\bm{B}=\sum_{i,j,k}A_{\cdots,i,j,k}B_{k,j,i,\cdots}
$$
